lead_paragraph: Rio 2016 organizers said on Tuesday there was no possibility the vote to award the Olympic Games to the Brazilian city could have been tainted, after French prosecutors said they had extended their corruption investigation.

headline.print_headline: Rio 2016 Organisers Exclude Possibility Games Vote Rigged
